{"title":"0029. 两数相除","date":"2020-01-14T17:34:05.106Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Jan 15, 2020","L":"01/15/2020","MM-DD":"01-15"},"updated":"2020-01-14T17:34:05.106Z","content":"<p><a href=\"leetcode/0029-en\">English</a>｜ 简体中文</p>\n<h2 id=\"题目描述\">题目描述<a href=\"leetcode/0029#题目描述\"></a></h2><p>给定两个整数，被除数 <code>dividend</code> 和除数 <code>divisor</code>。将两数相除，要求不使用乘法、除法和 mod 运算符。</p>\n<p>返回被除数 <code>dividend</code> 除以除数 <code>divisor</code> 得到的商。</p>\n<p><strong>示例 1：</strong></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>输入：</strong> dividend = 10, divisor = 3<br><strong>输出：</strong> 3</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><strong>示例 2：</strong></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>输入：</strong> dividend = 7, divisor = -3<br><strong>输出：</strong> -2</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><strong>说明：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>被除数和除数均为 32 位有符号整数。</li>\n<li>除数不为 0。</li>\n<li>假设我们的环境只能存储 32 位有符号整数，其数值范围是 [−2^31,  2^31 − 1]。本题中，如果除法结果溢出，则返回 2^31 − 1。</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"题解\">题解<a href=\"leetcode/0029#题解\"></a></h2><figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title\">Solution</span> </span>&#123;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">2</span></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">func</span> <span class=\"title\">divide</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"number\">_</span> dividend: Int, <span class=\"number\">_</span> divisor: Int)</span></span> -&gt; <span class=\"type\">Int</span> &#123;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">3</span></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">let</span> <span class=\"type\">INT_MAX</span> = <span class=\"type\">Int</span>(<span class=\"type\">INT32_MAX</span>)</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">4</span></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> divisor == <span class=\"number\">0</span> &#123;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">5</span></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"type\">INT_MAX</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">6</span></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">7</span></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">let</span> flag = (dividend &gt; <span class=\"number\">0</span>) == (divisor &gt; <span class=\"number\">0</span>)</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">8</span></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">var</span> d1 = <span class=\"built_in\">abs</span>(dividend), d2 = <span class=\"built_in\">abs</span>(divisor), <span class=\"built_in\">count</span> = <span class=\"number\">0</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">9</span></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">while</span> d1 &gt;= d2 &#123;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">10</span></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">var</span> shift = <span class=\"number\">0</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">11</span></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">while</span> d1 &gt;= d2 &lt;&lt; shift &#123;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">12</span></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">                shift += <span class=\"number\">1</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">13</span></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">14</span></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">            d1 -= d2 &lt;&lt; (shift - <span class=\"number\">1</span>)</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">15</span></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"built_in\">count</span> += <span class=\"number\">1</span> &lt;&lt; (shift - <span class=\"number\">1</span>)</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">16</span></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">17</span></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"built_in\">count</span> &gt; <span class=\"type\">INT_MAX</span> &amp;&amp; flag &#123;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">18</span></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"type\">INT_MAX</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">19</span></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">20</span></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> flag ? <span class=\"built_in\">count</span> : -<span class=\"built_in\">count</span></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">21</span></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">22</span></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n","link":"leetcode/0029","plink":"https://blog.fiteen.top/leetcode/0029/","toc":[{"title":"题目描述","id":"题目描述","index":"1"},{"title":"题解","id":"题解","index":"2"}],"copyright":{"author":"FiTeen","link":"<a href=\"https://blog.fiteen.top/leetcode/0029/\" title=\"0029. 两数相除\">https://blog.fiteen.top/leetcode/0029/</a>","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International (<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)"}}